name: The world seen through my eyes
description:
After so much suffering I was blind. It was already impossible for me to perceive things, darkness was part of my life and nothingness was my only reality.
But like a miracle, one day, among all the black, I saw a green flash, and behind it a line of colors. The black was turning white and the forms returned to take my reality.
Nothing was flat anymore, there were circles, squares and pointed triangles, all kinds of shapes and colors coexisted in harmony, even with black.
But even having all this back, nothing remained the only real thing.
